class Ionic:
    """Ionic radius class. Stores: charge, spin, coordination"""
    def __init__(self, charge=0, coordination="N/A", radius=0.0):
        self.charge = charge
        self.coordination = coordination
        self.radius = radius
        


[docs]
    def set_radius(self, value: float):
        self.radius = value
